trait-SignLanguage-name = Sign Language
trait-SignLanguage-desc =
    You can understand and use Tau-Ceti Basic Sign Language (TCB-SL).
    If you are mute for any reason, you can still communicate with sign language.

trait-Tradeband-name = Tradeband
trait-Tradeband-desc =
    Descended from latin and romance languages of old Earth - Tradeband remains the main tongue of the upper class of humanity.
    The language sounds elegant and well structured to most ears. It remains in popular use with traders - diplomats - and those seeking to hold onto a piece of a romantic past.

trait-Freespeak-name = Freespeak (Gutter)
trait-Freespeak-desc =
    A multi-rooted language used by renegades and frontiersmen that descended from Hindi and various other Earth languages. It sounds rather unique to non-native speakers.
    It serves as a common cultural identity on the frontier, and speakers of this language boldly declare themselves as free spirits.

trait-Elyran-name = Elyran Standard
trait-Elyran-desc =
    Elyran Standard is the official tongue of the Republic of Elyra.
    Constructed using elements of Farsi - Arabic - and Turkish - influence from all three of these languages can be seen throughout its grammar and vocabulary.

trait-Ratvarian-name = Ratvarian
trait-Ratvarian-desc =
    The language of the cult of Ratvar. Enigmatic, guttural, and difficult to pronounce.
    With some effort it can be understood by those not affiliated with the cult, but for you it comes naturally.

